hwEthernetARPMIB.name: hwEthernetARPMIB

revisions.description: Add ARP remote backup fail trap at 2014-04-23.
Fix the errors checked by a tool.
The initial revision of this MIB module.

hwEthernetARPMIB.contactinfo: Huawei Industrial Base Bantian, Longgang Shenzhen 518129 People's Republic of China Website: http://www.huawei.com Email: support@huawei.com
hwEthernetARPMIB.description: This MIB describes objects used for managing Ethernet ARP, including ARP Speed-limit,ARP Limit etc.

hwEthernetARPAntiAttackLog.name: hwEthernetARPAntiAttackLog
hwEthernetARPAntiAttackLog.description: To prevent log and trap from being attacked, the function is not enabled by default.

hwEthernetARPLearningStrict.name: hwEthernetARPLearningStrict
hwEthernetARPLearningStrict.description: Indicates the ARP strict learning. In this way, routers can learn ARP entries only from the arp reply in response to the arp requrest send by the router.

hwEthernetARPSpeedLimitTable.description: The table contains the configuration information of Ethernet ARP Speed limit slot. The information includes type, speedvalue, sourceip and destip.

hwEthernetARPSpeedLimitEntry.name: hwEthernetARPSpeedLimitEntry
hwEthernetARPSpeedLimitEntry.description: The table contains the configuration information of Ethernet ARP Speed limit slot. The information includes type, speedvalue, sourceip and destip.

hwEthernetARPLimitSlot.description: The slot of ARP Speed Limit.

hwEthernetARPLimitType.name: hwEthernetARPLimitType
hwEthernetARPLimitType.description: The Type of ARP Speed Limit.

hwEthernetARPLimitIPType.name: hwEthernetARPLimitIPType
hwEthernetARPLimitIPType.description: ARP speed limit is performed on a source or a destination IP address.

hwEthernetARPLimitSpeedValue.name: hwEthernetARPLimitSpeedValue
hwEthernetARPLimitSpeedValue.description: The Speed Value of ARP Speed Limit.

hwEthernetARPSpeedLimitIfIndex.name: hwEthernetARPSpeedLimitIfIndex

hwEthernetARPSpeedLimitConfigured.name: hwEthernetARPSpeedLimitConfigured
hwEthernetARPSpeedLimitConfigured.description: The Configured Speed Limit Value of ARP Speed Limit.

hwEthernetARPSpeedLimitCurrent.name: hwEthernetARPSpeedLimitCurrent
hwEthernetARPSpeedLimitCurrent.description: The Current Speed Limit Value of ARP Speed Limit.

hwEthernetARPSpeedLimitType.name: hwEthernetARPSpeedLimitType
hwEthernetARPSpeedLimitType.description: The Type of ARP Speed Limit.

hwEthernetARPSpeedLimitSrcIPAddr.name: hwEthernetARPSpeedLimitSrcIPAddr
hwEthernetARPSpeedLimitSrcIPAddr.description: The Source IP address of ARP Speed Limit.

hwEthernetARPSpeedLimitDstIPAddr.name: hwEthernetARPSpeedLimitDstIPAddr
hwEthernetARPSpeedLimitDstIPAddr.description: The Destination IP address of ARP Speed Limit.

hwEthernetARPSpeedLimitVPNinstance.name: hwEthernetARPSpeedLimitVPNinstance
hwEthernetARPSpeedLimitVPNinstance.description: The VPN-instance name of ARP Speed Limit.

hwEthernetARPStaticsTable.name: hwEthernetARPStaticsTable
hwEthernetARPStaticsTable.description: A table contains the statistics about Ethernet ARP. The statistics include number of received ARP packets, number of received ARP-MISS packets, number of learned ARP packets, number of discarded ARP packets caused by the ARP limit, the number of discarded ARP-MISS packets caused by the limit and the number of discarded ARP and ARP-MISS packets caused by other reasons.

hwEthernetARPStaticsEntry.name: hwEthernetARPStaticsEntry
hwEthernetARPStaticsEntry.description: A table contains the statistics about Ethernet ARP. The statistics include number of received ARP packets, number of received ARP-MISS packets, number of learned ARP packets, number of discarded ARP packets caused by the ARP limit, the number of discarded ARP-MISS packets caused by the limit and the number of discarded ARP and ARP-MISS packets caused by other reasons.

hwEthernetARPStaticsSlot.name: hwEthernetARPStaticsSlot
hwEthernetARPStaticsSlot.description: The slot about which the ARP statistics are displayed.

hwEthernetARPStaticsLearnTotal.name: hwEthernetARPStaticsLearnTotal
hwEthernetARPStaticsLearnTotal.description: The total number of the learned ARP packets.

hwEthernetARPDropForLimit.name: hwEthernetARPDropForLimit
hwEthernetARPDropForLimit.description: The number of discarded packets caused by limit.

hwEthernetARPDropForARPSuppress.name: hwEthernetARPDropForARPSuppress
hwEthernetARPDropForARPSuppress.description: The number of discarded packets caused by the ARP suppress.

hwEthernetARPDropForARPMissSuppress.name: hwEthernetARPDropForARPMissSuppress
hwEthernetARPDropForARPMissSuppress.description: The number of discarded packets caused by the ARP-MISS suppress.

hwEthernetARPDropForOther.name: hwEthernetARPDropForOther
hwEthernetARPDropForOther.description: The number of discarded ARP packets caused by other reasons.

hwEthernetARPMissDropForOther.name: hwEthernetARPMissDropForOther
hwEthernetARPMissDropForOther.description: The number of discarded ARP-MISS caused by other reasons.

hwEthernetARPRcvNum.name: hwEthernetARPRcvNum
hwEthernetARPRcvNum.description: The number of received ARP packets.

hwEthernetARPStaticsOperation.name: hwEthernetARPStaticsOperation
hwEthernetARPStaticsOperation.description: resets the statistics about Ethernet ARP.

hwEthernetARPDropForARPProxySuppress.name: hwEthernetARPDropForARPProxySuppress
hwEthernetARPDropForARPProxySuppress.description: The number of discarded packets caused by the ARP-PROXY suppress.

hwEthARPLimitTable.description: Configure the ARP limit based on interfaces or VLANs.

hwEthARPLimitEntry.name: hwEthARPLimitEntry
hwEthARPLimitEntry.description: Configure the ARP limit based on interfaces or VLANs.

hwEthARPLimitCfgIfindex.name: hwEthARPLimitCfgIfindex
hwEthARPLimitCfgIfindex.description: The interface on which the limit is configured.

hwEthARPVLANFirst.name: hwEthARPVLANFirst
hwEthARPVLANFirst.description: The VLAN to which Layer 2 interfaces belong.

hwEthARPVLANLast.name: hwEthARPVLANLast
hwEthARPVLANLast.description: The VLAN to which Layer 2 interfaces belong.

hwEthARPLimitNum.name: hwEthARPLimitNum
hwEthARPLimitNum.description: The value of the ARP limit.

hwEthARPLimitRowStatus.name: hwEthARPLimitRowStatus
hwEthARPLimitRowStatus.description: The running status of the ARP limit table.

hwEthernetARPLearningStrictInterfaceTabl.name: hwEthernetARPLearningStrictInterfaceTable
hwEthernetARPLearningStrictInterfaceTabl.description: Configure the ARP Learning Strict based on interfaces.

hwEthernetARPLearningStrictInterfaceEntr.name: hwEthernetARPLearningStrictInterfaceEntry
hwEthernetARPLearningStrictInterfaceEntr.description: Configure the ARP Learning Strict based on interfaces.

hwEthernetARPLearningStrictIfindex.name: hwEthernetARPLearningStrictIfindex
hwEthernetARPLearningStrictIfindex.description: The interface on which the ARP Learning Strict be configured.

hwEthernetARPLearningStrictState.name: hwEthernetARPLearningStrictState
hwEthernetARPLearningStrictState.description: The ARP Learning Strict State be configured.

hwEthernetARPLearningStrictRowStatus.name: hwEthernetARPLearningStrictRowStatus
hwEthernetARPLearningStrictRowStatus.description: The running status of the ARP Learning Strict table.

hwArpLinkInterfaceTable.name: hwArpLinkInterfaceTable
hwArpLinkInterfaceTable.description: Config ARP link interface: hwArpLinkIfIndex: interface index hwArpLinkPeerIp: peer ip hwArpLinkDetectTime: detection time between two ARP packects hwArpLinkDetectTimes: detection times of ARP packects hwArpLinkDetectMode: detection mode hwArpLinkStatus: interface status hwArpLinkRowStatus: the row status of this row.

hwArpLinkInterfaceEntry.name: hwArpLinkInterfaceEntry
hwArpLinkInterfaceEntry.description: Config ARP link interface: hwArpLinkIfIndex: interface index hwArpLinkPeerIp: peer ip hwArpLinkDetectTime: detection time between two ARP packects hwArpLinkDetectTimes: detection times of ARP packects hwArpLinkDetectMode: detection mode hwArpLinkStatus: interface status hwArpLinkRowStatus: the row status of this row.

hwArpLinkIfIndex.name: hwArpLinkIfIndex
hwArpLinkIfIndex.description: The index of interface which is configed to be linked by ARP, the zero value is invalid.

hwArpLinkPeerIp.name: hwArpLinkPeerIp
hwArpLinkPeerIp.description: The IP address which ARP detecting packet will send to. When creating a new record or modifying the peer ip address, a check for this ip will be generated. If it is invalid, that operation will be not applicable.

hwArpLinkDetectTime.name: hwArpLinkDetectTime
hwArpLinkDetectTime.description: The interval time for two ARP packets are sent to detect the peer's interface status, this time unit is millisecond. The valid range is from 200 to 10000, and the default value is 1000.

hwArpLinkDetectTimes.name: hwArpLinkDetectTimes
hwArpLinkDetectTimes.description: After the max detecting times for ARP packet is sent to, and there is not any response, the sender can judge the peer interface is down. Then, setting the status of current interface down. The valid range is from 1 to 10, and the default value is 3.

hwArpLinkDetectMode.name: hwArpLinkDetectMode
hwArpLinkDetectMode.description: The detecting mode for ARP linking interface. If the mode is loose and its status is down, current interface just wait to receive the ARP packet, when received peer's arp packet, current interface status is up. If mode is strict, current interface sends ARP detecting packet to peer actively, and shutdown itself, if these is no response from peer after the retry times. If status of current interface is up, it will send ARP packet to detect the status of peer actively, whenever the mode is loose or strict.

hwArpLinkStatus.name: hwArpLinkStatus
hwArpLinkStatus.description: The status of interface linked by ARP. This value can not be set anytime.

hwArpLinkRowStatus.name: hwArpLinkRowStatus
hwArpLinkRowStatus.description: The row status of ARP link table. The detail can be found from the rowstatus definition.

hwArpEntryExpireControlTable.name: hwArpEntryExpireControlTable
hwArpEntryExpireControlTable.description: The value of the object identifies the parameters of ARP aging detection, such as ARP detection mode, start time, detection times. At present, only the ARP detection mode and ARP fake-entry expire time can be configured. hwArpEntryExpireIfIndex: indicates the interface index. hwArpEntryExpireDetectMode: indicates the unicast or broadcast ARP aging detection mode. hwArpEntryExpireFakeTime: indicates the expire time of ARP fake entry.

hwArpEntryExpireControlEntry.name: hwArpEntryExpireControlEntry
hwArpEntryExpireControlEntry.description: The value of the object identifies the parameters of ARP aging detection, such as ARP detection mode, start time, detection times. At present, only the ARP detection mode and ARP fake-entry expire time can be configured. hwArpEntryExpireIfIndex: indicates the interface index. hwArpEntryExpireDetectMode: indicates the unicast or broadcast ARP aging detection mode. hwArpEntryExpireFakeTime: indicates the expire time of ARP fake entry.

hwArpEntryExpireIfIndex.name: hwArpEntryExpireIfIndex
hwArpEntryExpireIfIndex.description: This object indicates the index of an interface on which ARP aging detection parameters are set. The value 0 is invalid.

hwArpEntryExpireDetectMode.name: hwArpEntryExpireDetectMode
hwArpEntryExpireDetectMode.description: This object indicates the ARP aging detection mode. In unicast ARP detection mode, unicast ARP detection packets are sent before ARP ages. In broadcast ARP detection mode, broadcast ARP detection packets are sent before ARP ages. By default, the system adopts the broadcast ARP detection mode.

hwArpEntryExpireFakeTime.name: hwArpEntryExpireFakeTime
hwArpEntryExpireFakeTime.description: This object indicates the expire time of ARP fake entry. The valid range is from 1 to 36000, and the default value is 1.

hwArpDynTable.name: hwArpDynTable
hwArpDynTable.description: The value of the object identifies the items of ARP table, such as IP address of ARP items, VPN instance name of ARP items, MAC address of ARP items, VLAN information of ARP items, expire time of ARP items. hwArpDynEntryIfIndex: indicates the interface index. hwArpDynEntryIpAdd: indicates the IP address. hwArpDynEntryVrf: indicates the VPN instance name. hwArpDynEntryMacAdd: indicates the MAC address. hwArpDynEntryVlanId: indicates the VLAN of ARP item. hwArpDynEntryCeVlanId: indicates the CE VLAN of ARP item. hwArpDynEntryOutIfIndex: indicates the forwarding interface. hwArpDynEntryExpireTime: indicates the expire time of ARP item.

hwArpDynEntry.name: hwArpDynEntry
hwArpDynEntry.description: The value of the object identifies the items of dynamic ARP table, such as IP address of ARP items, VPN instance name of ARP items, MAC address of ARP items, VLAN information of ARP items, expire time of ARP items. hwArpDynEntryIfIndex: indicates the interface index. hwArpDynEntryIpAdd: indicates the IP address. hwArpDynEntryVrf: indicates the VPN instance name. hwArpDynEntryMacAdd: indicates the MAC address. hwArpDynEntryVlanId: indicates the VLAN of ARP item. hwArpDynEntryCeVlanId: indicates the CE VLAN of ARP item. hwArpDynEntryOutIfIndex: indicates the forwarding interface. hwArpDynEntryExpireTime: indicates the expire time of ARP item.

hwArpDynIfIndex.name: hwArpDynIfIndex
hwArpDynIfIndex.description: The logic forwarding interface. The value 0 is invalid.

hwArpDynIpAdd.name: hwArpDynIpAdd
hwArpDynIpAdd.description: This object indicates the IP address of an ARP items. The value 0 is invalid.

hwArpDynVrf.name: hwArpDynVrf
hwArpDynVrf.description: This object indicates the VPN name of an ARP items.

hwArpDynMacAdd.name: hwArpDynMacAdd
hwArpDynMacAdd.description: This object indicates the MAC address of an ARP items.

hwArpDynVlanId.name: hwArpDynVlanId
hwArpDynVlanId.description: This object indicates the VLAN of an ARP items.

hwArpDynCeVlanId.name: hwArpDynCeVlanId
hwArpDynCeVlanId.description: This object indicates the CE VLAN of an ARP items.

hwArpDynExpireTime.name: hwArpDynExpireTime
hwArpDynExpireTime.description: This object indicates the expire time of an ARP items.

hwArpCfgTable.name: hwArpCfgTable
hwArpCfgTable.description: The value of the object identifies the items of static ARP table, such as IP address of ARP items, VPN instance name of ARP items, MAC address of ARP items, VLAN information of ARP items. hwArpDynEntryIpAdd: indicates the IP address. hwArpDynEntryVrf: indicates the VPN instance name. hwArpDynEntryMacAdd: indicates the MAC address. hwArpDynEntryVlanId: indicates the VLAN of ARP item. hwArpDynEntryCeVlanId: indicates the CE VLAN of ARP item. hwArpDynEntryOutIfIndex: indicates the forwarding interface.

hwArpCfgEntry.name: hwArpCfgEntry
hwArpCfgEntry.description: The value of the object identifies the items of static ARP table, such as IP address of ARP items, VPN instance name of ARP items, MAC address of ARP items, VLAN information of ARP items. hwArpDynEntryIpAdd: indicates the IP address. hwArpDynEntryVrf: indicates the VPN instance name. hwArpDynEntryMacAdd: indicates the MAC address. hwArpDynEntryVlanId: indicates the VLAN of ARP item. hwArpDynEntryCeVlanId: indicates the CE VLAN of ARP item. hwArpDynEntryOutIfIndex: indicates the forwarding interface.

hwArpCfgIpAdd.name: hwArpCfgIpAdd
hwArpCfgIpAdd.description: This object indicates the IP address of an ARP items. The value 0 is invalid.

hwArpCfgMacAdd.name: hwArpCfgMacAdd
hwArpCfgMacAdd.description: This object indicates the MAC address of an ARP items.

hwArpCfgVrf.name: hwArpCfgVrf
hwArpCfgVrf.description: This object indicates the VPN name of an ARP items.

hwArpCfgVlanId.name: hwArpCfgVlanId

hwArpCfgCeVlanId.name: hwArpCfgCeVlanId
hwArpCfgCeVlanId.description: This object indicates the CE VLAN of an ARP items.

hwArpCfgRowstatus.name: hwArpCfgRowstatus
hwArpCfgRowstatus.description: This object indicates the row status of an static ARP item.

hwEthernetARPAntiAttackStatus.description: This object indicates the status of the ARP anti-attack.

hwEthernetARPAntiGateWayConflict.name: hwEthernetARPAntiGateWayConflict
hwEthernetARPAntiGateWayConflict.description: This object indicates the status of the ARP anti-gateway-conflict.

hwEthernetARPAntiGatewayConflictIpAddres.name: hwEthernetARPAntiGatewayConflictIpAddress

hwEthernetARPAntiGatewayConflictMacAddre.name: hwEthernetARPAntiGatewayConflictMacAddress
hwEthernetARPAntiGatewayConflictMacAddre.description: This object indicates the MAC of the attack-source.

hwARPArpGratuitousSendInterval.description: This object indicates the interval of the gratuitous-arp send. The value ranges from 1 to 86400, in second, with default value 90.

hwEthernetARPThresholdDynamicNumber.name: hwEthernetARPThresholdDynamicNumber

hwEthernetARPThresholdStaticNumber.name: hwEthernetARPThresholdStaticNumber

hwEthernetARPIPConflictLocalMAC.name: hwEthernetARPIPConflictLocalMAC
hwEthernetARPIPConflictLocalMAC.description: This object indicates the MAC before conflict.

hwEthernetARPIPConflictLocalVLAN.description: This object indicates the VLAN before conflict.

hwEthernetARPIPConflictLocalCEVLAN.name: hwEthernetARPIPConflictLocalCEVLAN
hwEthernetARPIPConflictLocalCEVLAN.description: This object indicates the CE VLAN before conflict.

hwEthernetARPIPConflictReceiveInterfaceN.name: hwEthernetARPIPConflictReceiveInterfaceName
hwEthernetARPIPConflictReceiveInterfaceN.description: This object indicates the conflict interface.

hwEthernetARPIPConflictReceiveCEVLAN.description: This object indicates the CE VLAN of the received packet.

hwEthernetARPIPConflictType.name: hwEthernetARPIPConflictType
hwEthernetARPIPConflictType.description: This object indicates the conflict type.

hwEthernetARPReceiveDstIPAddr.name: hwEthernetARPReceiveDstIPAddr
hwEthernetARPReceiveDstIPAddr.description: This object indicates the destination IP address of the received packet.

hwEthernetARPReceiveDstMAC.name: hwEthernetARPReceiveDstMAC
hwEthernetARPReceiveDstMAC.description: This object indicates the destination MAC of the received packet.

hwEthernetARPLearnStopTable.name: hwEthernetARPLearnStopTable
hwEthernetARPLearnStopTable.description: The value of the object identifies the parameters of ARP learning disable threshold. hwEthernetARPLearnStopSlot: indicates the slot. hwEthernetARPLearnStopThreshold: indicates the threshold usage of memory for learning ARP.

hwEthernetARPLearnStopEntry.name: hwEthernetARPLearnStopEntry
hwEthernetARPLearnStopEntry.description: The value of the object identifies the parameters of of ARP learning disable threshold. hwEthernetARPLearnStopSlot: indicates the slot of the alarm generated. hwEthernetARPLearnStopThreshold: indicates the threshold usage of memory for learning ARP.

hwEthernetARPLearnStopSlot.name: hwEthernetARPLearnStopSlot
hwEthernetARPLearnStopSlot.description: This object indicates the the slot of the alarm generated.

hwEthernetARPLearnStopThreshold.name: hwEthernetARPLearnStopThreshold
hwEthernetARPLearnStopThreshold.description: This object indicates the threshold usage of memory for learning ARP.

hwArpStatisticsTable.name: hwArpStatisticsTable
hwArpStatisticsTable.description: The table contains the arp information of the interfaces.

hwArpStatisticsEntry.name: hwArpStatisticsEntry
hwArpStatisticsEntry.description: The entry contains the arp information of the interfaces.

hwArpStatisticsSlot.name: hwArpStatisticsSlot
hwArpStatisticsSlot.description: The slot of ARP Statics Verbose.

hwArpStatisticsType.name: hwArpStatisticsType
hwArpStatisticsType.description: The Type of Interface Learn ARP.

hwArpStatisticsAvailableCount.name: hwArpStatisticsAvailableCount

hwEthernetARPSpeedLimitAlarm.description: Trap information about ARP speed limit: interface index, current configured limit number, current received number, limit type (ARP, ARP-MISS), source IP address, destination IP address, VPN instance.

hwEthernetARPAntiAttackAlarm.name: hwEthernetARPAntiAttackAlarm
hwEthernetARPAntiAttackAlarm.description: Trap information about ARP anti-attack: IP address, MAC, VLAN id, interface index.

hwEthernetARPAntiGatewayConflictAlarm.name: hwEthernetARPAntiGatewayConflictAlarm
hwEthernetARPAntiGatewayConflictAlarm.description: Trap information about ARP anti-attack: IP address, MAC, VLAN ID, interface index.

hwEthernetARPThresholdExceedAlarm.name: hwEthernetARPThresholdExceedAlarm
hwEthernetARPThresholdExceedAlarm.description: Trap information about ARP exceed threshold: slot, threshold, number of dynamic ARP, number of static ARP.

hwEthernetARPThresholdResumeAlarm.name: hwEthernetARPThresholdResumeAlarm
hwEthernetARPThresholdResumeAlarm.description: Trap information about ARP resume threshold: slot, threshold, number of dynamic ARP, number of static ARP.

hwEthernetARPIPConflictEvent.name: hwEthernetARPIPConflictEvent
hwEthernetARPIPConflictEvent.description: Trap information about ARP IP conflict.
